==English==
===Etymology===
Originally in plural, from Old French [[brachez]], plural of [[brachet]], a diminutive of Provençal [[brac]], from Old Frankish.

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/bræʧ/}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun|brach|braches}}
